Measure type: [475] Restriction on entry into free circulation
Measure components: Condition [B1] Presentation of a certificate/licence/document : Document [Y] Action [29] Import/export allowed after control : ||Condition [B2] Presentation of a certificate/licence/document : Document [C] Action [29] Import/export allowed after control : ||Condition [B3] Presentation of a certificate/licence/document : Action [09] Import/export not allowed after control :
Conditions: CD997: (Conditions) The import shall be subject to the presentation of a declaration as indicated on Annex of (EU) Regulation 284/2011. The Declaration is required if products contain polyamide parts or melamine parts intended to come into contact with foodstuff, or that come into contact with foodstuff when used according to their purpose, originating in or consigned from the People’s Republic of China and Hong Kong Special Administrative Region, China
